{"tid":987810,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國啲廢老特別鍾意話人唔識揸筷子","createTime":"2019-01-19T15:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T16:07:15.000Z","uid":184220,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"33052e98bc6ec3869aee7a2e3a437eae92dfee67","tid":987810,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"有次去食飯 老母就介紹個呀叔比我識 話佢大有來頭<br />\n咁我就打聲招呼 就繼續食嘢 點知佢就大聲講<br />\n「怕怕羞羞咁 筷子都唔識揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我反駁 「夾到咪得囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n咁佢就走去第張枱到 又聽到佢話人唔識揸筷子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗 屌 關你撚事咩 又唔係夾餸比你食<br />\n<br />\n利申：至少唔會合埋筷子<br />\n乜撚食物都夾到<br />\n力度夾撚死大笨象"},{"pid":"b87ebcd9acd2771fbf9d3d9ad76902122747cbec","tid":987810,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"好似我妹咁夾唔到呢？"},{"pid":"6ed02d53e478a4e58b6463fcbd4b3d6fae803183","tid":987810,"uid":184220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b87ebcd9acd2771fbf9d3d9ad76902122747cbec","tid":987810,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"好似我妹咁夾唔到呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚知"},{"pid":"242c599972025c41b5c5bdd90ec8cb5456e9bf19","tid":987810,"uid":225846,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ed02d53e478a4e58b6463fcbd4b3d6fae803183","tid":987810,"uid":184220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b87ebcd9acd2771fbf9d3d9ad76902122747cbec","tid":987810,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"好似我妹咁夾唔到呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"唔撚知"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"咁你就收皮啦"},{"pid":"51d69318d60c8592e34999b630d32567c2dd5f44","tid":987810,"uid":184220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242c599972025c41b5c5bdd9